        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Pretrial Release Reporting Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Bureau of Justice Statistics to submit a report to Congress on individuals who are granted bail or pretrial release from state courts and are charged with violent felony offenses (e.g., murder or rape). </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
